data.description: Updated and renovated home on 6th hole of Golf Club at Fleming Island. New roof in 2020, new AC in 2015, new hot water heater in 2021.  Quartz Cambria 12' ceilings in Great Room.  Three way split floor plan.  Sun room with marble floor overlooks the golf.  Engineered hardwood in four rooms including Brazilian Tigerwood in great room. Washer and Dryer can stay. New hospital in Fleming Island 1 mile away.  Two swim parks, tennis, golf available (semi private course), community activities at Fleming Island Plantation.  Popular restaurant at the golf club.   Lowest priced single story home on golf course in NE Florida of its size.  Termite bond in place. Seller is a Florida Real Estate Broker
